data.title: Photos: Wikipedia Founder Jimmy Wales
data.meta_description: Jimmy Wales is an American Internet entrepreneur best known for helping to start up the web-based encyclopedia, Wikipedia
data.text:
Front Man

As Wikipedia's public profile grew, Wales' role evolved from co-founder to site promoter and spokesman. In 2003, he set up the Wikimedia Foundation (WMF), a non-profit organization whose purpose is to establish general policy for the encyclopdia and its sister projects. Wales' work for the foundation includes apperances to promote it at computer and educational conferences.
